stateDiagram-v2
    title Workflow: ReAct цикл агента планирования

    [*] --> Receive_Input: POST /api/chat или /api/plan

    Receive_Input --> Guardrail_Check: validation + injection check

    Guardrail_Check --> Reject: injection detected
    Guardrail_Check --> NLP_Parse: текстовый запрос
    Guardrail_Check --> Anonymize: структурированные задачи

    NLP_Parse --> Anonymize: extract_tasks_from_text()

    Anonymize --> Init_State: Анонимизированные задачи + suggested_start

    state ReAct_Cycle {
        [*] --> think
        think --> execute: LLM вернул tool_calls
        think --> [*]: LLM ответил текстом

        execute --> think: Итерация < 25
        execute --> [*]: Итерация >= 25 или все задачи размещены

        note right of think
            LLM решает:
            - get_current_time
            - get_date
            - get_events
            - validate_schedule
            - create_event
        end note

        note right of execute
            Выполнение инструментов:
            - Rate limit check
            - Security validation
            - Tool execution
            - Update state
        end note
    }

    Reject --> [*]: Error 500

    Init_State --> ReAct_Cycle
    ReAct_Cycle --> Evaluate: Цикл завершён
    Evaluate --> Save_Metrics: quality_score, latency, tokens, cost
    Save_Metrics --> Langfuse_Trace: optional
    Langfuse_Trace --> Return_Plan: metrics.json + langfuse
    Return_Plan --> [*]: JSON ответ
